Memories;;1995;;PG-13;;Animation,Sci-Fi,Thriller;;7.6;;Amber Lee Connors,Kôji Morimoto,Tensai Okamura;;Marc Swint,Robbie Daymond,Frank Todaro,Laura Post,Derek Stephen Prince,Alexa N. Careccia,Kirk Thornton,Martha Harms,Michael Sinterniklaas,Stephanie Sheh,Stephen Fu,Chris Guerrero,Gianni Matragrano,Steven Kelly,Kira Buckland,Jack Britton,Mike Pollock,Ellen-Ray Hennessy;;"Memories" is made up of three separate science-fiction stories. In the first, "Magnetic Rose," four space travelers are drawn into an abandoned spaceship that contains a world created by one woman's memories. In "Stink Bomb," a young lab assistant accidentally transforms himself into a human biological weapon set on a direct course for Tôkyô. The final episode, "Cannon Fodder," depicts a day in the life of a city whose entire purpose is the firing of cannons at an unseen enemy.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113799/